              "text": {
                "content": "This is an empyrical study conducted using 67 students from China. A recommender system made suggestions on art knowledge for students to take. The authors evaluated whether the recommender increased the learners awareness about art appreciation. Satisfaction results show that students were happy with the model and that the fact that the activities were done out of school was a big motivating factor.",
